             </ul>
            </div>
           </div>
           <div id="nav_menu-41" class="widget clearfix widget_nav_menu">
            <h3 class="widgettitle">Prepare for VMI</h3>
            <div class="menu-prepare-container">
             <ul id="menu-prepare" class="menu">
              <li id="menu-item-5190" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-5190"><a href="http://admissions.vmi.edu/apply/prepare/requirements/">Admission Requirements</a></li> 
              <li id="menu-item-5191" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-5191"><a href="http://admissions.vmi.edu/apply/prepare/">High School Preparation</a></li> 
              <li id="menu-item-3580" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-3580"><a href="http://admissions.vmi.edu/apply/prepare/im-accepted-now-what/">I’m accepted. Now what?</a></li> 
              <li id="menu-item-6061" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-6061"><a href="http://admissions.vmi.edu/apply/prepare/im-accepted-now-what/admissions-status-definitions/">Admissions Status Definitions</a></li> 
             </ul>
            </div>
           </div>
          </div>
         </div>
         <div class="flex_column av_one_half   avia-builder-el-3  el_after_av_one_fourth  el_before_av_one_fourth  ">
          <div style="padding-bottom:10px;" class="av-special-heading av-special-heading-h3    avia-builder-el-4  el_before_av_textblock  avia-builder-el-first  ">
           <h3 class="av-special-heading-tag" itemprop="headline">Applying to VMI</h3>
           <div class="special-heading-border">
            <div class="special-heading-inner-border"></div>
           </div>
          </div> 
          <section class="av_textblock_section" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork">
           <div class="avia_textblock " itemprop="text">
            <p>VMI’s application procedure is the same whether you are applying for the first time, as a transfer student, or as an international student.</p> 
            <p>New cadets are enrolled only at the beginning of the academic year in August. Please review the application instructions below to ensure that you include all required documents with your submission.</p> 
           </div>
          </section> 
          <section class="av_textblock_section" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork">
           <div class="avia_textblock " itemprop="text">
            <h5><strong>Deadlines</strong></h5> 
            <p>Early Decision: Nov. 15<br> Regular Decision: Feb. 1</p> 
           </div>
          </section> 
          <div class="avia-button-wrap avia-button-left  avia-builder-el-7  el_after_av_textblock  el_before_av_button ">
           <a href="https://postview.vmi.edu/VMIpages/On_Line_Application_Instructions.html" class="avia-button  avia-icon_select-yes-left-icon avia-color-blue avia-size-medium avia-position-left " target="_blank"><span class="avia_button_icon avia_button_icon_left " aria-hidden="true" data-av_icon="" data-av_iconfont="entypo-fontello"></span><span class="avia_iconbox_title">Apply Online in Post View</span></a>
          </div> 
          <div class="avia-button-wrap avia-button-left  avia-builder-el-8  el_after_av_button  avia-builder-el-last ">
           <a href="http://admissions.vmi.edu/?p=4639" class="avia-button  avia-icon_select-yes-left-icon avia-color-green avia-size-medium avia-position-left " target="_blank"><span class="avia_button_icon avia_button_icon_left " aria-hidden="true" data-av_icon="" data-av_iconfont="entypo-fontello"></span><span class="avia_iconbox_title">Download Application</span></a>
          </div>
         </div>
         <div class="flex_column av_one_fourth   avia-builder-el-9  el_after_av_one_half  avia-builder-el-last  ">
          <article class="iconbox iconbox_left   avia-builder-el-10  el_before_av_button  avia-builder-el-first " itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork">
           <div class="iconbox_content">
            <header class="entry-content-header">
             <div class="iconbox_icon heading-color" aria-hidden="true" data-av_icon="" data-av_iconfont="entypo-fontello"></div>
             <h3 class="iconbox_content_title" itemprop="headline"><a href="https://postview.vmi.edu/VMIpages/On_Line_Application_Instructions.html" title="Post View" target="_blank">Post View</a></h3>
            </header>
            <div class="iconbox_content_container " itemprop="text">
             <p>To apply online or check application status, you will need to create an account in Post View, VMI’s internal system used to process applications and financial aid.</p> 
             <p>Use Post View to complete your application, check&nbsp; status, and review financial aid.</p> 
            </div>
           </div>
           <footer class="entry-footer"></footer>
          </article> 
          <div class="avia-button-wrap avia-button-left  avia-builder-el-11  el_after_av_icon_box  avia-builder-el-last ">
           <a href="https://postview.vmi.edu/VMIpages/On_Line_Application_check_status_instructions.html" class="avia-button  avia-icon_select-yes-left-icon avia-color-theme-color-subtle avia-size-medium avia-position-left " target="_blank"><span class="avia_button_icon avia_button_icon_left " aria-hidden="true" data-av_icon="" data-av_iconfont="entypo-fontello"></span><span class="avia_iconbox_title">Check Status in Post View </span></a>
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
      </main>
